  <brief_title>Study of Efficacy of Induction Chemotherapy With Gemcitabine and Carboplatin for Operable Non-small-cell Lung Cancer Before Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of the Response Rate of Induction Chemotherapy With Gemcitabine and Carboplatin for Operable Non-small Cell Lung Cancer Before Surgery</official_title>
