  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study the activity of chemotherapy with Gemzar-carboplatin in the preoperative setting for
      operable stages of non-small-cell lung cancer and to identify novel molecular markers
      correlated with chemosensitivity and prognosis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
